! Title: Epic Games / Fortnite full block (ABP/AdGuard)
! Description: Blocks Epic Games services (store, launcher, Fortnite, EOS) and common CDNs/shorteners
! Version: 2025-09-06
! Syntax: Adblock Plus

! core epic domains (covers all subdomains)
||epicgames.com^
||epicgames.dev^
||epicgamescdn.com^

! launcher / store / auth (redundant with apex, kept for clarity)
||store.epicgames.com^
||launcher.epicgames.com^
||accounts.epicgames.com^
||oauth.epicgames.com^
||tracking.epicgames.com^
||logs.epicgames.com^
||static-assets-prod.epicgames.com^
||assets.on.epicgames.com^

! service cluster (redundant with apex)
||*.ol.epicgames.com^
||account-public-service-prod*.ol.epicgames.com^
||friends-public-service-prod*.ol.epicgames.com^
||entitlement-public-service-prod*.ol.epicgames.com^
||catalog-public-service-prod*.ol.epicgames.com^
||lightswitch-public-service-prod*.ol.epicgames.com^
||launcher-public-service-prod*.ol.epicgames.com^
||datastorage-public-service-*.ol.epicgames.com^

! downloads / CDN used by the launcher
||download*.epicgames.com^
||epicgames-download*.akamaized.net^

! fortnite
||fortnite.com^
||fn.gg^
||cdn2.unrealengine.com^/fortnite/

! epic online services (EOS)
||api.epicgames.dev^
||eos.epicgames.com^

! easy anti-cheat (used by Epic titles)
||easy.ac^
||eac-cdn.com^

! short links often used by epic
||epic.gm^
||egs.link^

